description: Let Alexa help you learn things new and unknown facts about computers! Simply ask Alexa to ask the skill "computer facts" for a fact. Here are a few simple invocations, "Alexa ask computer facts for a computer fact" or "Alexa ask computer facts to give me a computer trivia"
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask computer facts to tell me a computer fact
Alexa ask computer facts to give me a computer fact
name: Computer Facts
shortDescription: A skill set that provides interesting facts about computers.
